title: NFL Around the League: July 26th, 2013

description:
Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal are back at it again, discussing the latest news from around the league and the major stories trending on NFL.com, including the Eric Wright saga and the Seahawks' troubling news about Percy Harvin.
